		<h1>2020 MTV<br>Video Music Awards</h1>
		<p style="font-weight: bold;text-align: left;margin-left: unset;">Date: May 24, 2020 • Madison Square Garden<br><br>Taking place at the Madison Square Garden in New York City, the historic MTV Video Music Awards is the first awards show of 2020 after the devastating COVID-19 pandemic.<br><br>
		A celebration of music and the creative geniuses and works that intensify the music through visuals, the MTV Video Music Awards honors the best of the best when it comes to videos of all relevant genres, the songs they empower, and the people behind every video. Attracting millions of viewers from across the globe, a performance in this coveted awards show is a guaranteed boost for all works from albums to singles.<br><br>
